metadata.name: Blue Mimetik
metadata.description:
Reborn NFT. On August 2022 Opensea banned me from the platform as other artists in Cuba and countries like Venezuela and Iran. 
This collection aims to return the NFTs to the owners. 

Blue Mimetik.  
Sold: 5/9/2021 
to: 
0x7d19667db8d6d2d4fabc0bc2b2c9c7dedfd3a5a8

Description:  
This is the first unique piece of this collection of 7. Cuban Doors series meet NFT Guild, inspired by @mondoir work and ideas about NFTs and digital art.
